title: Rambo The Video Game: Baker Team
notes: Game works flawlessly once you get it running. On launch the game does not find language files. To get around it delete GameLauncher.exe and then rename Rambo.exe to GameLauncher.exe. If you want to change the games settings you can do it by manually editing the file /data/config.lua

title: Rambo The Video Game: Baker Team
notes: Ran out of the box with native like performance, no work around needed.
